ADR + mockup primary citation MANDATORY ÎNAINTE write\" (2× threshold met chat trecut S2 spec procedural ADR 026 §9 violation + chat-current S3 v1 quadruple violation invented files/functions/state fields) + §AR.21 LOCKED V1 verbatim \"Prompts that cite §AR.20 mandatory grep MUST embed grep output snippets verbatim as inline evidence per file/function referenced\" (CC autonomous Opus originated rule via S3 v1 halt raport §5 + Daniel explicit LOCK V1 confirm acord chat-current). §AR.21 = §AR.20 strengthen meta-pattern citation-without-enforcement NU rule nouă orthogonală. First execution post-codification Bundle 1 S3.C `d41e111` + S3.D `47729ed` LANDED atomic 2/2 ZERO slip surfaced validation effective. §AR.1-§AR.19 + §AR.20-§AR.22 candidate preserved invariant unchanged"},{"date":"2026-05-13d","note":"APPEND §AR.22 candidat DISCRETE-BLOCKS DISCIPLINE 1× threshold met explicit chat-current chat ACASĂ post Bundle 3 V1 narrow + Bundle 3 follow-up LANDED — slip Bundle 3B spec §4 al meu conflate L987-991 preview button block + L1007-1008 tombstone CEVA NU MERGE drill blocuri non-contigue separate ~16 linii unrelated screen content; CC autonomous push-back productive scribe-side saved over-removal corect call conservativ preserved tombstone different screen different concern; Bundle 3 follow-up spec §9 explicit learning verbatim \"When PROMPT_CC targets non-contiguous code blocks, spec MUST enumerate each block as DISCRETE section (Block N at L<line>) with independent str_replace per block + independent grep evidence + independent view pre-edit verify. NO line-range span across non-contiguous content.\" + successful end-to-end 3 discrete blocks Block 1+2+3 independent str_replace application. §AR.22 candidat 1× threshold met (NU 2× pentru codify încă per §AR.* codification rule 2× minimum, watch pentru next occurrence + flag Daniel review fresh chat). §AR.21 3rd consecutive validation effective post-codification Bundle 1 + Bundle 3 + Bundle 3 follow-up LANDED first-attempt ZERO slip surfaced. §AR.1-§AR.21 LOCKED V1 + §AR.22 candidate preserved invariant unchanged"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"wiki/concepts/anti-recurrence-rules.md"},"smart_blocks:wiki/concepts/anti-recurrence-rules.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"qq0s5o","at":1778663581497},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.12769257,-0.0249886,-0.04477124,0.0040226,-0.07018632,0.00643218,-0.01157427,0.03018251,0.01984488,0.00976869,-0.00204604,-0.02580455,0.03028101,-0.00169801,0.02486556,0.02363088,-0.02069205,0.04709857,-0.02592472,-0.01629408,0.08208387,0.02032304,-0.07675529,-0.01027906,0.02489613,0.0213498,-0.03982003,-0.04240622,-0.05363726,-0.2499752,-0.02555966,-0.00239271,-0.03105273,-0.01619707,-0.01599989,-0.01560243,-0.06652872,0.05954165,-0.07255504,0.0874373,0.0142254,0.04209821,0.04251672,-0.03824696,0.0119318,-0.03109076,-0.0487099,-0.00926218,-0.06148013,-0.02119048,-0.01708029,-0.0217455,-0.01630811,0.01348779,0.03031166,0.0273698,0.09173775,0.04470212,0.00214076,0.07250027,0.07304201,-0.00780011,-0.21422037,0.06843457,-0.018473,0.00111825,-0.02231276,-0.042082,-0.00226139,0.03783512,0.01462124,-0.01774382,-0.00841812,0.05593055,0.00931429,0.0269492,-0.01373088,-0.0213027,0.00157152,0.01658166,0.00059342,0.02611016,-0.00130111,-0.01188378,-0.02544777,-0.05886848,0.02846483,-0.0297652,0.01117042,0.00066882,-0.03722069,0.02389738,0.09700842,0.03185133,-0.04147625,0.01884361,-0.03646749,0.01338329,-0.06500474,0.09985128,-0.0441623,0.03539846,-0.03616022,0.02414618,0.02385115,0.00673001,0.01720418,-0.07433487,-0.0288873,0.0208233,-0.00507533,0.00622883,0.1089,-0.0994373,0.01075229,0.10872652,0.05295804,0.04335908,0.05622539,0.02319827,0.00153819,0.012256,0.03973139,-0.04136996,-0.0011677,-0.00528351,0.04927767,0.03204588,0.05285487,0.05801652,0.06308952,0.00337455,-0.01381942,0.01146185,0.03160027,0.01538155,-0.03287534,0.02728585,0.01742758,-0.06119362,-0.04411859,-0.05232012,0.01549228,-0.0456223,