candidate 2× threshold cumulative preserved invariant unchanged"},{"date":"2026-05-13d","note":"APPEND §AR.22 candidat DISCRETE-BLOCKS DISCIPLINE 1× threshold met explicit chat-current chat ACASĂ post Bundle 3 V1 narrow + Bundle 3 follow-up LANDED — slip Bundle 3B spec §4 al meu conflate L987-991 preview button block + L1007-1008 tombstone CEVA NU MERGE drill blocuri non-contigue separate ~16 linii unrelated screen content; CC autonomous push-back productive scribe-side saved over-removal corect call conservativ preserved tombstone different screen different concern; Bundle 3 follow-up spec §9 explicit learning verbatim \"When PROMPT_CC targets non-contiguous code blocks, spec MUST enumerate each block as DISCRETE section (Block N at L<line>) with independent str_replace per block + independent grep evidence + independent view pre-edit verify. NO line-range span across non-contiguous content.\" + successful end-to-end 3 discrete blocks Block 1+2+3 independent str_replace application. §AR.22 candidat 1× threshold met (NU 2× pentru codify încă per §AR.* codification rule 2× minimum, watch pentru next occurrence + flag Daniel review fresh chat). §AR.21 3rd consecutive validation effective post-codification Bundle 1 + Bundle 3 + Bundle 3 follow-up LANDED first-attempt ZERO slip surfaced. §AR.1-§AR.21 LOCKED V1 + §AR.22 candidate preserved invariant unchanged"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"wiki/concepts/anti-recurrence-rules.md"},"smart_blocks:wiki/concepts/anti-recurrence-rules.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"rkcwfw","at":1778668137441},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.12881808,-0.02375272,-0.0455645,0.00458351,-0.06887667,0.00648374,-0.01276329,0.03201407,0.01873608,0.00788967,-0.00295023,-0.02683527,0.03093122,-0.00174458,0.02563757,0.02040815,-0.02185541,0.04868929,-0.02160366,-0.01767142,0.0829193,0.02136695,-0.07604893,-0.01117659,0.02764236,0.02211849,-0.03796584,-0.04297065,-0.055035,-0.250212