1 codification 2× threshold met explicit chat-current chat ACASĂ post S3 Guards Bundle 1 LANDED — §AR.20 LOCKED V1 verbatim \"PROMPT_CC src/ reference verify ADR + mockup primary citation MANDATORY ÎNAINTE write\" (2× threshold met chat trecut S2 spec procedural ADR 026 §9 violation + chat-current S3 v1 quadruple violation invented files/functions/state fields) + §AR.21 LOCKED V1 verbatim \"Prompts that cite §AR.20 mandatory grep MUST embed grep output snippets verbatim as inline evidence per file/function referenced\" (CC autonomous Opus originated rule via S3 v1 halt raport §5 + Daniel explicit LOCK V1 confirm acord chat-current). §AR.21 = §AR.20 strengthen meta-pattern citation-without-enforcement NU rule nouă orthogonală. First execution post-codification Bundle 1 S3.C `d41e111` + S3.D `47729ed` LANDED atomic 2/2 ZERO slip surfaced validation effective. §AR.1-§AR.19 + §AR.20-§AR.22 candidate preserved invariant unchanged"},{"date":"2026-05-13e","note":"APPEND §AR.21 4th consecutive validation effective + §AR.22 candidat 2× threshold cumulative potential chat-current chat ACASĂ post Bundle 4 workout-preview + per-exercise refusal flow + mid-session augmentation LANDED `429c189` single atomic commit clean — §AR.21 4th consecutive validation effective post-codification ZERO slip surfaced (Bundle 1 + Bundle 3 + Bundle 3 follow-up + Bundle 4) PROMPT_CC ~720 LOC structurat §AR.21 grep evidence verbatim inline mandatory pe 13 file/funcție rule continues effective as designed; §AR.22 candidat DISCRETE-BLOCKS DISCIPLINE potentially 2× threshold met cumulative now (Bundle 3 follow-up 3 discrete blocks + Bundle 4 12-block split A-L explicit per file/funcție = 2× threshold met explicit chat-current) — codify next handover dacă pattern persists chat NEW post Daniel review explicit fresh chat decizie strategic Bundle 5 ADR amendment SMART_ROUTING_v2 dedicat. 3 slip patterns chat-current mid-execute scribe-mode marked (origin-rooted cascade tracking DOM stable identity slip surface mid-execute fixes exhaustion semantics când row replace muta exercițiul curent + XSS test laxity + chain tests sufficient alternatives) — Co-CTO accumulation tactical-as-strategic safety prompts slip cooperative push-back smiley NEW pattern catalysator chat-current Daniel verbatim *\"ce am eu de discutat? ca vad ca fiecare chat mai imi adauga cate ceva de clarificat cu daniel :))\"* anti-confirmation theater. §AR.1-§AR.21 LOCKED V1 + §AR.22 candidate 2× threshold cumulative preserved invariant unchanged"},{"date":"2026-05-13d","note":"APPEND §AR.22 candidat DISCRETE-BLOCKS DISCIPLINE 1× threshold met explicit chat-current chat ACASĂ post Bundle 3 V1 narrow + Bundle 3 follow-up LANDED — slip Bundle 3B spec §4 al meu conflate L987-991 preview button block + L1007-1008 tombstone CEVA NU MERGE drill blocuri non-contigue separate ~16 linii unrelated screen content; CC autonomous push-back productive scribe-side saved over-removal corect call conservativ preserved tombstone different screen different concern; Bundle 3 follow-up spec §9 explicit learning verbatim \"When PROMPT_CC targets non-contiguous code blocks, spec MUST enumerate each block as DISCRETE section (Block N at L<line>) with independent str_replace per block + independent grep evidence + independent view pre-edit verify. NO line-range span across non-contiguous content.\" + successful end-to-end 3 discrete blocks Block 1+2+3 independent str_replace application. §AR.22 candidat 1× threshold met (NU 2× pentru codify încă per §AR.* codification rule 2× minimum, watch pentru next occurrence + flag Daniel review fresh chat). §AR.21 3rd consecutive validation effective post-codification Bundle 1 + Bundle 3 + Bundle 3 follow-up LANDED first-attempt ZERO slip surfaced. §AR.1-§AR.21 LOCKED V1 + §AR.22 candidate preserved invariant unchanged"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"wiki/concepts/anti-recurrence-rules.md"},"smart_blocks:wiki/concepts/anti-recurrence-rules.md#Anti-Recurrence Ru